      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="vertical-align:top; height:43px;">
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">Application Notes</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">This law has a high maximum-velocity, high maximum-acceleration, but Zero </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Cross-Over" styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">crossover jerk</link><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> .</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">At the start and end of this Motion-Law, the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Y-axis</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true"> does not change very much with a significant </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">X–axis</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true"> change - 0.02% Y-axis with 5% X-axis change. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">Therefore, to accurately reproduce the Motion-Law, it needs precise machining, a large cam, or an encoder with a high resolution. If possible, increase the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-SegmentEditor-Segment-Width" styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">segment-width</link><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">to reduce the maximum-velocity and jerk values.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Dynamic Performance</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">: </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">This Motion-Law is recommended in applications where the period ratio is between about 5 and 10.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Pressure Angle Considerations</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">This</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">has a relatively large maximum-acceleration and maximum velocity, which will increase the maximum pressure-angle.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Drive Torques</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">It has a high peak torque.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">Motion-Law Coefficients</text></para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName-indent"><text styleclass="VariableName-indent" translate="true">Cv = 2.000</text></para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName-indent"><text styleclass="VariableName-indent" translate="true">Ca = ±8.000</text></para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName-indent"><text styleclass="VariableName-indent" translate="true">Cj = ±52.265</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
        </td>
